06/11/2003
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- The international community is satisfied with the progress of the collection campaign for illegal weapons, spokespersons for the EU, the OSCE and the EU military mission Concordia said at a joint press conference Wednesday (5 November). The officials said the campaign is proceeding peacefully and on schedule, now that all 123 municipalities have joined the effort. They also urged stronger support on the part of local authorities, to ensure the initiative succeeds. (Dnevnik, Utrinski Vesnik - 06/11/03; MIA, A1 TV - 05/11/03)
